‚úÖ CREATE MAVEN PROJECT IN ECLIPSE
Open Eclipse
File ‚Üí New ‚Üí Other
Type Maven ‚Üí select Maven Project ‚Üí Next
Leave default workspace ‚Üí Next
Uncheck ‚ÄúShow the latest version of archetypes only‚Äù
Select:
org.apache.maven.archetypes ‚Üí maven-archetype-quickstart (1.4)
Next
Fill in:
Group Id: com.example
Artifact Id: my_java
Finish
--->BUILD + RUN
Right-click project ‚Üí Run As ‚Üí Maven clean
Right-click project ‚Üí Run As ‚Üí Maven install
Right-click App.java ‚Üí Run As ‚Üí Java Application
--->PUSH TO GITHUB
Go to GitHub ‚Üí New repository
Repository name: my_java
Add .gitignore ‚Üí choose Maven
Create repository


